Titolo: Star Fox Zero

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Star Fox Zero is a 3D rail shooter video game developed by Nintendo and PlatinumGames for the Wii U. It is the sixth installment in the Star Fox series and the second reboot of the franchise after Star Fox 64 (1997). Formally announced at E3 2015, the game was released in April 2016 to mixed critical reception, with the most polarizing aspect of the game being its control scheme. A standalone tower defense game, titled Star Fox Guard, was bundled with the game.

Genere: Rail shooter

Valutazione: 69
